content:
spoiler free review of #aquietplace
• not ground-breaking/genre-defining but a satisfying watch

• a few loose plot threads that don't detract from the overall 
• paves the way for a 2nd blunt-krasinski outing

name: Roxy Striar
content: I just saw #AQuietPlace & I won’t ever sleep again. The usage of sound is unlike anything I’ve ever heard. Even if you’re not a horror fan, this is a MUST see. The performances make you cry & scream. Just YES to everything. As a fellow NSHS alum @johnkrasinski you’re #goals .pic.twitter.com/LQEq8YtxJB

name: CineMovie TV
content: I haven't seen an old school horror movie in a long time. Loved #AQuietPlace. Very satisfying and original creature feature. The funny part was you can hear the audience munching on their popcorn during the quiet open. #stayquiet
